      "chapter": "第一章",
      "node_name": "第一个问题",
      "background": null,
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "text": "欢迎大家参加外星人遇上黄果树的产品\n这是一个实景解谜游戏",
          "insert_image": "/uploads/1780481236787-0a220380.png",
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "小典",
          "speaker_avatar": "/uploads/1780475066672-2a682994.png"
        },
        {
          "text": "需要大家动动脑筋去解谜\n对了忘记自我介绍了",
          "insert_image": null,
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "小典",
          "speaker_avatar": "/uploads/1780475074631-97af9db4.png"
        },
        {
          "text": "我是来自陈典兔事侦探务所的小典\n这次我们需要调查失踪的蛋",
          "insert_image": null,
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "小典",
          "speaker_avatar": "/uploads/1780475081299-b9c42885.png"
        },
        {
          "text": "有一天我醒来就发现我的蛋不！见！了！\n我也不知道为什么它不见了\n你们一定要帮帮我...找回丢失的蛋....",
          "insert_image": "/uploads/1780479440007-50b33c50.png",
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "火苗龙",
          "speaker_avatar": "/uploads/1780475086882-6f4b182d.png"
        },
        {
          "text": "求你们帮我找回来！我……我什么都愿意做",
          "insert_image": "/uploads/1780480494213-dcc8fa3b.png",
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "火苗龙",
          "speaker_avatar": null
        },
        {
          "text": "十二颗蛋，偷蛋的人很懂行——专挑苗寨最不能忘的事下手...",
          "insert_image": "/uploads/1780987745975-0f3e5ca7.png",
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "小典",
          "speaker_avatar": null
        },
        {
          "text": "委托成立：【寻找十二蛋】\n委托人：火苗龙\n请前往地图上的第一个地点\n解开谜题 ，获得线索",
          "insert_image": null,
          "typewriter_speed": 20,
          "speaker": "【系统提示】",
          "speaker_avatar": null
        }
      ],
